name: BNBC
description: Digitalised tradable assets for personal usage on the MintMe website, which value is backed by purchasing power in BNB with total profits (Profits = Income - Cost) and having a constant of stable income of investments. BNBC is created on the MintMe blockchain but deployed on the Binance Smart Chain and is not affiliated with Binance in any ways. BNBC aims to be a stable, but profitable trading token, with more interactivity coming in the near future.
